Isaiah-- you know that.

00:13:58.450 --> 00:14:00.260 align:middle line:84%
We could go on
and on about this.

00:14:00.260 --> 00:14:04.070 align:middle line:84%
But I really think Marcion
was right and so does Sarah.

00:14:04.070 --> 00:14:07.760 align:middle line:84%
And I'm bringing the issue into
a novelistic form, hopefully,

00:14:07.760 --> 00:14:10.860 align:middle line:84%
that it will reach a wider
audience than nonfiction

00:14:10.860 --> 00:14:13.150 align:middle line:84%
