00:28:04.400 --> 00:28:04.920 align:middle line:90%
with this.

00:28:04.920 --> 00:28:06.711 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So I asked
you a couple of times.

00:28:06.711 --> 00:28:08.392 align:middle line:84%
Can you talk about
the black mass?

00:28:08.392 --> 00:28:09.350 align:middle line:90%
What is the black mass?

00:28:09.350 --> 00:28:10.016 align:middle line:90%
>>HAND CLOW: OK.

00:28:10.016 --> 00:28:13.760 align:middle line:84%
The black mass is
a reputed thing

00:28:13.760 --> 00:28:15.930 align:middle line:84%
that has been going on
since the Middle Ages

00:28:15.930 --> 00:28:19.040 align:middle line:84%
as far as I can tell, maybe
back as far as 500 BC,

00:28:19.040 --> 00:28:23.060 align:middle line:84%
where the old system, goddess
system of hirogamos, which

00:28:23.060 --> 00:28:26.870 align:middle line:84%
is the sexual intercourse
between the priest or the corn

00:28:26.870 --> 00:28:28.530 align:middle line:84%
God or whatever
with the goddess.

00:28:28.530 --> 00:28:30.430 align:middle line:84%
A woman plays the
role of the goddess.

00:28:30.430 --> 00:28:32.320 align:middle line:90%
It's what creates fertility.

00:28:32.320 --> 00:28:34.900 align:middle line:84%
It's what creates the
functioning of the climate

00:28:34.900 --> 00:28:35.540 align:middle line:90%
cycles.

00:28:35.540 --> 00:28:39.670 align:middle line:84%
It's what creates healthy
birthing and healthy sense

00:28:39.670 --> 00:28:40.810 align:middle line:90%
of genetics.

00:28:40.810 --> 00:28:44.610 align:middle line:84%
And so what happened
with the black mass was,

00:28:44.610 --> 00:28:47.880 align:middle line:84%
there were rumors like
crazy, very credible rumors

00:28:47.880 --> 00:28:50.520 align:middle line:84%
that people took
the Catholic mass

00:28:50.520 --> 00:28:53.110 align:middle line:90%
and did a black mass ceremony.

00:28:53.110 --> 00:28:54.890 align:middle line:84%
And basically, this
involves a woman

00:28:54.890 --> 00:28:57.750 align:middle line:84%
being on the altar, sexual
intercourse on the altar,

00:28:57.750 --> 00:29:00.960 align:middle line:84%
so it's a reversal
of the Catholic mass.

00:29:00.960 --> 00:29:04.150 align:middle line:84%
And I really think
it's clear that this

00:29:04.150 --> 00:29:05.900 align:middle line:84%
has been going on for
hundreds of years,

00:29:05.900 --> 00:29:06.920 align:middle line:90%
but it's so under the cover.

00:29:06.920 --> 00:29:08.056 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: But you say
there's a purpose in terms

00:29:08.056 --> 00:29:10.974 align:middle line:84%
