and the use of this energy.

00:29:10.974 --> 00:29:13.390 align:middle line:84%
Explain that part, because I
thought that was interesting.

00:29:13.390 --> 00:29:14.450 align:middle line:84%
>>HAND CLOW: And
so that's where I'm

00:29:14.450 --> 00:29:16.040 align:middle line:84%
exploring it through
my characters.

00:29:16.040 --> 00:29:19.420 align:middle line:84%
And so Claudia,
Armando's old girlfriend,

00:29:19.420 --> 00:29:21.894 align:middle line:84%
is one of the people who
is one of the participants

00:29:21.894 --> 00:29:23.310 align:middle line:84%
in the black mass,
so I'm actually

00:29:23.310 --> 00:29:25.880 align:middle line:84%
exploring it through
their experience.

00:29:25.880 --> 00:29:27.580 align:middle line:84%
And all I've been
able to do with that

00:29:27.580 --> 00:29:29.830 align:middle line:84%
since this is really
undercover stuff,

00:29:29.830 --> 00:29:32.240 align:middle line:84%
but I really believe
this has been going on

00:29:32.240 --> 00:29:34.630 align:middle line:90%
and is still going on.

00:29:34.630 --> 00:29:37.200 align:middle line:84%
And I don't see it necessarily
as a negative thing.

00:29:37.200 --> 00:29:40.096 align:middle line:84%
It seems to be a reaction
to the control issues.

00:29:40.096 --> 00:29:41.720 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Well, is
it a transmutation--

00:29:41.720 --> 00:29:42.680 align:middle line:84%
>>HAND CLOW: It is
a transmutation.

00:29:42.680 --> 00:29:44.179 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: --of the
