00:29:44.179 --> 00:29:47.520 align:middle line:84%
being perpetuated kind of
above ground at the Vatican

00:29:47.520 --> 00:29:51.420 align:middle line:84%
by the church by grounding it
into the old goddess energy

00:29:51.420 --> 00:29:51.920 align:middle line:90%
fields?

00:29:51.920 --> 00:29:54.220 align:middle line:84%
>>HAND CLOW: I don't that people
in the church are doing it,

00:29:54.220 --> 00:29:54.890 align:middle line:90%
primarily.

00:29:54.890 --> 00:29:57.140 align:middle line:84%
I think it's people who
are very anti-church who

00:29:57.140 --> 00:29:58.140 align:middle line:90%
are participating in it.

00:29:58.140 --> 00:29:59.556 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: But I
mean they're doing

00:29:59.556 --> 00:30:01.860 align:middle line:84%
it to counter-effect
those energies in a sense.

00:30:01.860 --> 00:30:02.610 align:middle line:90%
>>HAND CLOW: Yeah.

00:30:02.610 --> 00:30:03.930 align:middle line:90%
I think so.

00:30:03.930 --> 00:30:08.350 align:middle line:84%
So I mean, I'd rather let
people experience this.

00:30:08.350 --> 00:30:11.150 align:middle line:84%
But I'm dealing with
all of these issues

00:30:11.150 --> 00:30:14.020 align:middle line:84%
like Sarah's visions,
the black mass,

00:30:14.020 --> 00:30:16.410 align:middle line:84%
the issue of masses going
on under the Vatican.

00:30:16.410 --> 00:30:19.520 align:middle line:84%
I'm dealing with all of them
from a fictional perspective

00:30:19.520 --> 00:30:20.980 align:middle line:84%
and a multi-dimensional
perspective

00:30:20.980 --> 00:30:22.490 align:middle line:84%
because I actually
think they can't

00:30:22.490 --> 00:30:24.650 align:middle line:90%
be understood any other way.

00:30:24.650 --> 00:30:27.450 align:middle line:84%
And regarding, for instance,
the issue of masses,

00:30:27.450 --> 00:30:31.190 align:middle line:84%
there's a description in the
book of caves under the Vatican

00:30:31.190 --> 00:30:34.180 align:middle line:84%
to the four directions
under the basilica where

00:30:34.180 --> 00:30:36.480 align:middle line:90%
masses are going on 24/7.

00:30:36.480 --> 00:30:39.470 align:middle line:84%
This was something that was
