00:30:39.470 --> 00:30:42.680 align:middle line:84%
and of course, I can't
reveal the source on this.

00:30:42.680 --> 00:30:45.700 align:middle line:84%
And so I -- years and years
ago, this was told to me like 30

00:30:45.700 --> 00:30:46.730 align:middle line:90%
years ago.

00:30:46.730 --> 00:30:49.170 align:middle line:84%
And so I've been thinking
about that ever since,

00:30:49.170 --> 00:30:53.016 align:middle line:84%
and I don't know how third
dimensional it actually is,

00:30:53.016 --> 00:30:54.890 align:middle line:84%
but I think there's
something going on there.

00:30:54.890 --> 00:30:58.390 align:middle line:84%
And so one of the things I
went after deeply in this novel

00:30:58.390 --> 00:31:01.640 align:middle line:84%
is what is really going on
with the power of the mass.

00:31:01.640 --> 00:31:04.850 align:middle line:84%
Even if it's not going on
24/7 under the Vatican,

00:31:04.850 --> 00:31:07.580 align:middle line:90%
it's going on globally 24/7.

00:31:07.580 --> 00:31:09.980 align:middle line:84%
So I'm really using the
Vatican just like a vortex,

00:31:09.980 --> 00:31:13.480 align:middle line:84%
like a grand square vortex,
and that's so interesting

00:31:13.480 --> 00:31:15.280 align:middle line:84%
because we're coming
up to a grand square

00:31:15.280 --> 00:31:18.290 align:middle line:84%
in April, a major
astrological grand square.

00:31:18.290 --> 00:31:20.000 align:middle line:84%
Because grand
squares bring things

00:31:20.000 --> 00:31:24.120 align:middle line:84%
into manifestation, and
so the Catholic church

00:31:24.120 --> 00:31:29.220 align:middle line:84%
has literally manifested
itself as a global power entity

00:31:29.220 --> 00:31:33.070 align:middle line:84%
by going all over the world
and taking over sacred sights.

00:31:33.070 --> 00:31:35.670 align:middle line:84%
All of the Catholic churches,
especially the oldest ones,

00:31:35.670 --> 00:31:40.610 align:middle line:84%
are all built on the top
of original power spots,

00:31:40.610 --> 00:31:43.387 align:middle line:84%
especially in the area of
the Magdalenian culture.

00:31:43.387 --> 00:31:43.970 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:31:43.970 --> 00:31:45.840 align:middle line:84%
And Notre-Dame, for
example, and others, yes.

00:31:45.840 --> 00:31:46.390 align:middle line:90%
>>HAND CLOW: That's right.

00:31:46.390 --> 00:31:47.223 align:middle line:90%
All of the churches.

00:31:47.223 --> 00:31:49.740 align:middle line:90%


00:31:49.740 --> 00:31:53.510 align:middle line:84%
And we have letters
from Augustine of Hippo

00:31:53.510 --> 00:31:56.560 align:middle line:84%
back in 600 AD
instructing the priests

00:31:56.560 --> 00:31:58.430 align:middle line:84%
as they went up
north into Germany

00:31:58.430 --> 00:32:00.100 align:middle line:84%
and went into
England and Scotland,

00:32:00.100 --> 00:32:03.320 align:middle line:84%
and all that, to find the
power spots of the people,

00:32:03.320 --> 00:32:06.210 align:middle line:84%
and get the land, and build
the church right there.

00:32:06.210 --> 00:32:10.060 align:middle line:84%
So what they've done is, they've
created this system of building

00:32:10.060 --> 00:32:13.100 align:middle line:84%
churches on power places,
and the churches usually

00:32:13.100 --> 00:32:14.100 align:middle line:90%
are fairly tall.

00:32:14.100 --> 00:32:17.490 align:middle line:84%
There's always a goal to have
a church be fairly tall so you

00:32:17.490 --> 00:32:20.790 align:middle line:84%
can activate the
power spot, which

00:32:20.790 --> 00:32:23.780 align:middle line:84%
is under the earth-- the
first and second dimension--

00:32:23.780 --> 00:32:28.430 align:middle line:84%
and then you can use the mass
to control this activation.

00:32:28.430 --> 00:32:30.230 align:middle line:84%
Now, when you think
about it with churches,

00:32:30.230 --> 00:32:33.060 align:middle line:84%
churches are like a
multi-dimensional cap

00:32:33.060 --> 00:32:34.520 align:middle line:90%
over Earth force.

00:32:34.520 --> 00:32:37.420 align:middle line:84%
So my issue is, what is
going on with the mass?

00:32:37.420 --> 00:32:39.080 align:middle line:84%
And the book is
working with the idea

00:32:39.080 --> 00:32:42.200 align:middle line:84%
that the mass was a
carry over of the Hebrew

00:32:42.200 --> 00:32:44.740 align:middle line:84%
sacrificial rituals,
which are coming

00:32:44.740 --> 00:32:48.460 align:middle line:84%
from the Canaanite sacrificial
rituals all the way back,

00:32:48.460 --> 00:32:50.065 align:middle line:84%
and I think it's
time to stop it.

00:32:50.065 --> 00:32:52.670 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Well, what
better way to stop it

00:32:52.670 --> 00:32:59.010 align:middle line:84%
than to have revealed these
distorted and dark practices

00:32:59.010 --> 00:33:01.320 align:middle line:84%
at a time when, as you
say astrologically,

