00:37:10.114 --> 00:37:11.280 align:middle line:90%
What about the whole notion.

00:37:11.280 --> 00:37:15.780 align:middle line:84%
You talk about these sacred
spots and the 12 degrees

00:37:15.780 --> 00:37:16.429 align:middle line:90%
longitudinally.

00:37:16.429 --> 00:37:17.220 align:middle line:90%
What is that about?

00:37:17.220 --> 00:37:17.970 align:middle line:90%
>>HAND CLOW: Yeah.

00:37:17.970 --> 00:37:23.130 align:middle line:84%
This is bringing in the work
of Carl Johan Calleman who

00:37:23.130 --> 00:37:26.320 align:middle line:84%
wrote about the whole issue of
nine underworlds, the creation

00:37:26.320 --> 00:37:30.230 align:middle line:84%
of the Mayan calendar going
back 16.4 billion years.

00:37:30.230 --> 00:37:33.480 align:middle line:84%
And one of the most
interesting concepts and ideas

00:37:33.480 --> 00:37:36.020 align:middle line:84%
that Calleman has
explored is the issue

00:37:36.020 --> 00:37:39.410 align:middle line:84%
of a midline at 12
degrees east longitude.

00:37:39.410 --> 00:37:41.730 align:middle line:84%
And this midline, if
you look at a map,

00:37:41.730 --> 00:37:45.340 align:middle line:84%
would run into Africa right
about where Gabon is located,

00:37:45.340 --> 00:37:47.520 align:middle line:84%
then it comes up
through Tunisia,

00:37:47.520 --> 00:37:49.010 align:middle line:84%
and then it comes
up through Italy,

00:37:49.010 --> 00:37:50.770 align:middle line:84%
and then it goes
up through Germany,

00:37:50.770 --> 00:37:53.400 align:middle line:84%
and up through Gothenburg,
and keeps going north.

00:37:53.400 --> 00:37:57.720 align:middle line:84%
And Calleman developed the
idea that on the eastern side

00:37:57.720 --> 00:38:00.280 align:middle line:84%
of this midline, there
were certain forces

00:38:00.280 --> 00:38:03.580 align:middle line:84%
playing on the Western side,
certain forces where at play,

00:38:03.580 --> 00:38:05.820 align:middle line:84%
and that there's
huge conflict that

00:38:05.820 --> 00:38:07.850 align:middle line:90%
gets activated at the midline.

00:38:07.850 --> 00:38:11.920 align:middle line:84%
So I got into this idea
because the Vatican is located

00:38:11.920 --> 00:38:17.120 align:middle line:84%
on the midline, and the
third Fatima prophecy says

00:38:17.120 --> 00:38:19.770 align:middle line:84%
that what's going to
happen is, the East is

00:38:19.770 --> 00:38:21.104 align:middle line:90%
going to conquer the West.

00:38:21.104 --> 00:38:22.520 align:middle line:84%
Now, I don't know
whether the East

00:38:22.520 --> 00:38:23.728 align:middle line:90%
is going to conquer the West.

00:38:23.728 --> 00:38:25.670 align:middle line:84%
If they do, it will be
the end of the planet,

00:38:25.670 --> 00:38:27.130 align:middle line:84%
and if the West
conquers the East,

00:38:27.130 --> 00:38:28.240 align:middle line:84%
it will be the
end of the planet.

00:38:28.240 --> 00:38:30.140 align:middle line:84%
And I think we're
going to continually go

00:38:30.140 --> 00:38:31.610 align:middle line:90%
back and forth like this.

00:38:31.610 --> 00:38:33.860 align:middle line:84%
But it shows that
tremendous conflict

00:38:33.860 --> 00:38:36.060 align:middle line:84%
that's operative
right at the midline.

00:38:36.060 --> 00:38:38.970 align:middle line:84%
And I think one of the ways
the Vatican has developed

00:38:38.970 --> 00:38:42.520 align:middle line:84%
global power is to play
with that polarity.

00:38:42.520 --> 00:38:44.700 align:middle line:84%
So then I'm dealing
with the issue

00:38:44.700 --> 00:38:47.330 align:middle line:84%
of under the Vatican and
the lower dimensions,

00:38:47.330 --> 00:38:49.810 align:middle line:84%
and the book is getting
into the underworld,

00:38:49.810 --> 00:38:51.910 align:middle line:84%
the issue of the
demons, all that.

00:38:51.910 --> 00:38:53.480 align:middle line:90%
So I'm playing with all of it.

00:38:53.480 --> 00:38:56.130 align:middle line:84%
And my main issue
with all of it is

00:38:56.130 --> 00:38:57.660 align:middle line:84%
trying to look at
it from a third

00:38:57.660 --> 00:38:59.880 align:middle line:84%
and a fourth dimensional
point of view,

00:38:59.880 --> 00:39:01.970 align:middle line:84%
because people get really
confused about this.

00:39:01.970 --> 00:39:04.520 align:middle line:84%
One example would be,
for, me David Icke

00:39:04.520 --> 00:39:05.920 align:middle line:84%
