00:39:54.160 --> 00:39:55.900 align:middle line:84%
So the characters are
playing with that,

00:39:55.900 --> 00:39:58.270 align:middle line:84%
like what does it take
to be a person who

00:39:58.270 --> 00:40:02.500 align:middle line:84%
is beyond being impacted by
fourth-dimensional forces.

00:40:02.500 --> 00:40:05.060 align:middle line:90%
So Simon's father is a Magus.

00:40:05.060 --> 00:40:09.320 align:middle line:84%
He's a Magus in a Jewish
line coming from Isaac Luria,

00:40:09.320 --> 00:40:11.445 align:middle line:84%
