00:42:29.400 --> 00:42:31.330 align:middle line:90%
what is it about that structure?

00:42:31.330 --> 00:42:33.830 align:middle line:84%
>>HAND CLOW: Well, think of
the black and white travertine

00:42:33.830 --> 00:42:35.220 align:middle line:90%
