the ultimate sort of yin

00:42:40.375 --> 00:42:43.520 align:middle line:84%
and yang and playing of
the dark and the light,

00:42:43.520 --> 00:42:46.510 align:middle line:84%
and it goes back to the days
of the medieval synthesis.

00:42:46.510 --> 00:42:50.110 align:middle line:84%
It was built between
about 1150 and 1300 AD

00:42:50.110 --> 00:42:52.420 align:middle line:84%
when the synthesis
was still powerful.

00:42:52.420 --> 00:42:54.320 align:middle line:90%
What's the medieval synthesis?

00:42:54.320 --> 00:42:56.870 align:middle line:84%
Well, back in the
Middle Ages, the church

00:42:56.870 --> 00:43:00.580 align:middle line:84%
had still not stomped
out the earlier cultures,

00:43:00.580 --> 00:43:03.210 align:middle line:84%
and Siena has the
strongest imprint

00:43:03.210 --> 00:43:06.280 align:middle line:84%
at this point in time of
the medieval synthesis

00:43:06.280 --> 00:43:08.350 align:middle line:84%
of any place on
the planet Earth.

00:43:08.350 --> 00:43:13.180 align:middle line:84%
And the way you can see this is
the town has these 17 contrade,

00:43:13.180 --> 00:43:16.430 align:middle line:84%
and the 17 contrade have
this medieval thing they do,

00:43:16.430 --> 00:43:20.050 align:middle line:84%
which is they have this
race called the Palio, which

00:43:20.050 --> 00:43:21.400 align:middle line:90%
is a horseback race.

00:43:21.400 --> 00:43:25.110 align:middle line:84%
And each one of the contrade
is a different animal,

00:43:25.110 --> 00:43:28.180 align:middle line:84%
and if it goes back to
the saving of the species.

00:43:28.180 --> 00:43:32.500 align:middle line:84%
The medieval synthesis
was profoundly ecological,

00:43:32.500 --> 00:43:34.756 align:middle line:84%
and those codes are
being protected by Siena.

00:43:34.756 --> 00:43:36.422 align:middle line:84%
